# The compiled program (target/deploy/*.so) and target/idl are committed on
# purpose so the PoC runs immediately with `yarn && yarn test`, no `anchor build`
# required. The program keypair stays ignored (see the repo-root .gitignore) — it
# isn't needed to run the tests, only to rebuild/redeploy to the same address.
